=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wirestock/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/ewa-manthey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ewa Manthey</a>, Commodities Strategist</em></p> <p>Copper has been under pressure despite Beijing\u2019s efforts to boost the economy, with Chinese domestic consumption remaining sluggish amid deflation threats and the prolonged property market crisis. The US election has further</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743662-trump-and-china-add-to-copper-headwinds-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:25:00"}, {"id": "4743643", "title": "Micron: A Solid Buy Into Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2009686025/image_2009686025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AI Bot On Phone. Machine Learning. Digital Mind Technology Concept\" data-id=\"2009686025\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"878px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2009686025/image_2009686025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2009686025/image_2009686025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2009686025/image_2009686025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2009686025/image_2009686025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://