,000 branches <span>throughout most of the United States,</span> <span><b>Bank of America Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAC\" title=\"Bank of America Corporation\">BAC</a></span>) is one of the world's biggest financial institutions, with a market cap of over $350 billion at the time of</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173572523/image_173572523.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743639-bank-of-america-a-buy-despite-seeming-overvaluation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:04:22"}, {"id": "4743655", "title": "Cognyte Software Ltd. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Cognyte Software Ltd. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106119\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743655-cognyte-software-ltd-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 20:56:28"}, {"id": "4743633", "title": "BE Semiconductor: A Market Leader With Enormous Dividend Growth Potential", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808243985/image_1808243985.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Futuristic microchip and digital data flowing. AI concept\" data-id=\"1808243985\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808243985/image_1808243985.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808243985/image_1808243985.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808243985/image_1808243985.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808